Package io.github.ai4ci.output

Class CSVMapper

java.lang.Object
io.github.ai4ci.output.CSVMapper
public abstract class CSVMapper extends Object
Mapper responsible for converting domain model objects into CSV DTOs.

This abstract MapStruct mapper centralises the logic used to produce CSV-friendly immutable transfer objects for reporting and downstream analysis. Typical inputs are outbreak, person and history objects and outputs are immutable CSV types defined in this package (for example ImmutableOutbreakCSV, ImmutableLineListCSV).

Downstream uses: the CSV DTOs produced by this mapper are consumed by reporting and analysis routines external to the core simulation. See the io.github.ai4ci.output package for the DTO types and the Outbreak and Person classes which provide the inputs to the mapper.

Author:
Rob Challen
